              text: 'IPTV Smarters Pro is a premium IPTV player app that lets you watch 20,000+ live TV channels, movies and series on any device including Firestick, Android, iPhone, and Smart TV.',
            },
          },
          {
            '@type': 'Question',
            name: 'How many channels are included in the IPTV subscription?',
            acceptedAnswer: {
              '@type': 'Answer',
              text: 'Our IPTV Smarters Pro subscription includes 20,000+ live channels and 100,000+ VOD movies and series in HD and 4K quality.',
            },
          },
          {
            '@type': 'Question',
            name: 'Which devices support IPTV Smarters Pro?',
            acceptedAnswer: {
              '@type': 'Answer',
              text: 'IPTV Smarters Pro works on Android, iPhone, iPad, Amazon Firestick, Fire TV, Samsung Smart TV, LG Smart TV, MAG Box, Windows PC and Mac.',
            },
          },
          {
            '@type': 'Question',
            name: 'Is there a free IPTV trial available?',
            acceptedAnswer: {
              '@type': 'Answer',
              text: 'Yes! We offer a free 24-hour IPTV trial with access to all 20,000+ channels and 100,000+ VOD content. No credit card required.',
            },
          },
          {
            '@type': 'Question',
            name: 'What payment methods do you accept?',
